        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards understanding climate change and its effects in various locations.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Atmosphere and weather, including atmospheric composition are included in Group 1801 Air quality, atmosphere and weather.
