      <skos:Concept rdf:about="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2413">
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Processed food products and beverages (excl. dairy products)</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:notation>2413</skos:notation>
        <skos:inScheme rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020"/>
        <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/24"/>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the manufacture of processed food and beverage products. It includes carcass meat, nutraceuticals and functional foods.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Production of unprocessed or semi-processed plant primary products is included in Division 26 Plant production and plant primary products.
b) Production of unprocessed or semi-processed animal primary products is included in Division 10 Animal production and animal primary products.
c) Processing of milk into dairy products is included in Group 2405 Dairy products.
d) Production of feed for animal consumption is included in Group 2414 Processed non-food agriculture products (excl. wood, paper and fibre).
e) Food safety is included in 2004 Public health (excl. specific population health).</skos:scopeNote>
