        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the manufacture and repair of transport equipment, including their components.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Internal hydrogen combustion engines are included in Group 1704 Energy transformation.
b) Construction of transport infrastructure is included in Division 12 Construction.
c) Transport infrastructure (other than its construction) is included in Division 27 Transport.</skos:scopeNote>
