        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards farming or breeding livestock. It includes beekeeping and pet breeding.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Preparation, handling, and storage of primary livestock products, e.g. unprocessed milk, raw wool, raw hides and skins, is included in Group 1006 Primary products from animals.
b) Animal welfare and livestock product traceability and quality assurance are included in Group 1099 Other animal production.
c) Manufacture of processed livestock products, e.g. processed milk and processed skins, is included in Division 24 Manufacturing.</skos:scopeNote>
