        <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/24"/>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the processing of wood, and the manufacture of wood products, paper and paper products.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Harvest and transportation of logs and forest products is included in Group 2602 Forestry.
b) Prefabrication of wooden buildings and the manufacture of wooden furniture are included in Group 2499 Other manufacturing.
c) Printing and publishing of newspapers and other media publications is included in Group 2205 Media services.</skos:scopeNote>
