        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the manufacture of chemical fertilisers and chemicals for the protection of crops and livestock.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Organic fertilisers and the manufacture of plant extracts which may be used as insecticides or repellents (e.g. pyrethrum) are included in Group 2414 Processed non-food agriculture products (excl. wood, paper and fibre).
b) Manufacture of veterinary pharmaceuticals is included in Group 2416 Veterinary pharmaceutical products.</skos:scopeNote>
