        <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/16"/>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the improvement of school and educational institution learning environments.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Improvement of learning outcomes of individual learners is included in Group 1601 Learner and learning.
b) Improvement of teaching and instruction techniques is included in Group 1603 Teaching and curriculum.
c) Curriculum improvement is included in Group 1603 Teaching and curriculum.
d) Improvement of education and training systems is included in Group 1603 Teaching and curriculum.
e) Development of school or educational institutional environments conducive to the education of Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islanders, Māori and Pacific Peoples are included in Groups 2102 Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander education, 2106 Māori education and 2110 Pacific Peoples education.</skos:scopeNote>
