        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards improving the characteristics and harvesting of fisheries caught in the wild for commercial or recreational reasons.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Improvement of the characteristics and harvesting of aquaculture fisheries is included in Group 1002 Fisheries - aquaculture.
