        <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/24"/>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the manufacture of industrial chemicals and related products, including those derived from oil and gas refining.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Mining, extraction, and processing of energy resources used for the manufacture of industrial chemicals and products and the production of chemicals intended for use as an energy source are included in Division 17 Energy.
b) Manufacture of agricultural chemicals is included in Group 2401 Agricultural chemicals.
c) Manufacture of human pharmaceutical products is included in Group 2408 Human pharmaceutical products.
d) Manufacture of veterinary pharmaceutical products is included in Group 2416 Veterinary pharmaceutical products.</skos:scopeNote>
