        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the manufacture of ceramics, glass and glass products and industrial mineral products, including clay, cement and concrete products. It includes R&amp;D directed towards the manufacture of plaster and non-metallic mineral products.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Mining, extraction, and first stage processing of stone, clay, sand and ores used for the manufacture of ceramics, glass and industrial mineral products are included in Division 25 Mineral resources (excl. energy resources).
b) Testing the performance and durability and life cycle of building materials is included in Group 1203 Construction materials performance and processes.</skos:scopeNote>
