        <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/24"/>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the manufacture of structural and sheet metal products, castings, machined and semi-finished fabricated metal products.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Basic metal products is included in Group 2402 Basic metal products (incl. smelting, rolling, drawing and extruding).
b) Prefabrication of metal buildings and manufacture of sheet metal furniture is included in Group 2499 Other manufacturing.
c) Testing of the performance, durability and life cycle of manufactured building materials is included in Division 12 Construction.</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:narrower rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/240701"/>
