        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the processing of agricultural products not intended for human consumption, other than wood, paper and fibre products.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Production of whole plants, plant parts, and unprocessed or semi-processed plant primary products used for plant extracts or extraction of essential oils is included in Division 26 Plant production and plant primary products.
b) Processing of agricultural products for food is included in Groups 2413 Processed food products and beverages (excl. dairy products) and 2405 Dairy products.
c) Production of products from natural rubber is included in Group 2409 Industrial chemicals and related products.</skos:scopeNote>
