        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards improving understanding, provision and delivery of education relating to Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander populations.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Educational needs of non-Indigenous populations are included in Group 1601 Learner and learning.
b) Inclusive education related to non-Indigenous populations are included in Group 1602 Schools and learning environments.
c) The understanding and provision of education related to Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander populations is included in Group 2102 Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander education Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander education.
d) The understanding and provision of education related to Māori populations is included in Group 2106 Māori education.</skos:scopeNote>
