    <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/12"/>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards the design, installation and maintenance of building services, as well as demolition and refurbishment.</skos:definition>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Energy conservation and efficiency in building management and services is included in Group 1701 Energy efficiency.
b) Provision of communications services is included in Group 2201 Communication technologies, systems and services.
c) Development and provision of property services (e.g. property development, real estate and alarm and surveillance services) are included in Group 1103 Property, business support services and trade.
d) Conservation of historic buildings and structures is included in Group Group 1304 Heritage.</skos:scopeNote>
