      <skos:Concept rdf:about="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/1006">
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Primary products from animals</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:notation>1006</skos:notation>
        <skos:inScheme rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020"/>
        <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/10"/>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers R&amp;D directed towards improving the preparation, handling or storage of primary animal products such as eggs, honey, raw wool, unprocessed or minimally processed fish or milk, and other animal fibres, hides and skins.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Improving the characteristics and harvesting of fisheries is included in Groups 1002 Fisheries - aquaculture and 1003 Fisheries - wild caught.
b) Raising livestock from which these products are obtained is included in Group 1004 Livestock raising.
c) Animal welfare is included in Group 1099 Other animal production.
d) Manufacture of processed products from primary animal products is included in Division 24 Manufacturing.
e) Transportation of live animals or animal products is included in Division 27 Transport.</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:narrower rdf:resource="https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/100601"/>
