    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This Division covers R&amp;D directed towards the development of defence or national security, and the development and testing of military or defence related equipment and materials. It includes R&amp;D undertaken for military reasons regardless of their content or whether they have secondary civil applications, and nuclear and space R&amp;D undertaken for military purposes.</skos:definition>
